itsprinzip, die eigenkapitalersetzenden Gesellschafterdarlehen.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 0aBusiness enterprisesxLaw and legislationzGermany. 0aBusiness enterpriseszGermany. 0aCommercial lawzGermanyxElectronic books. 0aCommercial lawzGermany. 4aAuslegung. 4aDeutschland. 4aFunktion. 4aGesellschaftsrecht. 7aLAW / Corporate.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Law - 2000 - 2014z9783110636208oZDB-23-GLA0 cprintz978311017082540uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311090184940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110901849423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110901849/original  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_LAEC  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-GLAc2000d2014